par
<sub xmlns:mml="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">F</sub>
 approximation algorithms for the singular value decomposition of an m times n matrix A with M non-zero entries that requires 2 passes over the data and runs in time O((M(k/epsi+k log k) + (n+m)(k/epsi+k log k)
